412
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:21,920
These were all General Ye's credits.

413
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:29,840
But this time, Beique's men helping Ye Dingzhi has nothing to do with this.

414
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:36,160
I'm afraid there's a bigger conspiracy behind this.

415
00:39:37,640 --> 00:39:39,460
 What conspiracy?

416
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:49,180
Shouldn't the Shadow Sect be telling me this?

417
00:39:57,200 --> 00:40:02,360
Go to Lei Mengsha. Let him make the trip.

418
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:03,940
Yes.

419
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:15,720
Not bad. I can see that you've already achieved something.

420
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:18,940
Now I can carry a zither and hurt people with its sound.

421
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:20,460
It's so elegant and impressive.

422
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:24,060
This technique you taught me is really awesome. What's its name?

423
00:41:24,060 --> 00:41:25,900
It's Xunian Technique of Beique.

424
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:28,340
Xunian Technique?

425
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,420
Yes.

426
00:41:29,420 --> 00:41:34,700
It's the most profound martial art in Beique and also the most difficult to master.

427
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:38,620
I've been practicing for years but only picked up the basics.

428
00:41:38,620 --> 00:41:40,380
But you're a natural martial artist.

429
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:42,500
You can master it naturally.

430
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:45,900
Xunian, Xunian, illusory and real. 
  (TN: xunian - false thoughts)

