00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:50,460
Just as the sound of the zither turns into blades,

432
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:53,920
Why did you have me learn this technique?

433
00:41:59,540 --> 00:42:07,720
I wanted to teach you this technique long ago so that you could save my father.

434
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:10,420
Then I changed my mind.

435
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:16,780
But Mister Li said there was no harm in teaching you.

436
00:42:16,780 --> 00:42:21,100
It was for after you mastered the 19 Embroidery Sword Techniques

437
00:42:21,100 --> 00:42:25,620
