438
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:30,480
I think this is the right time.

439
00:42:31,620 --> 00:42:36,060
I see. So when are we going to save your father?

440
00:42:36,060 --> 00:42:38,720
To Tian Wai Tian?

441
00:42:38,720 --> 00:42:41,760
It's not the right time. It's too dangerous.

442
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:46,780
Besides, if my father was out,

443
00:42:46,780 --> 00:42:53,720
it would be a catastrophe for Beili and the world.

444
00:42:55,980 --> 00:43:03,760
Though I truly miss him a lot.

445
00:43:05,340 --> 00:43:08,460
Yao'er, don't worry.

446
00:43:09,860 --> 00:43:14,380
Just wait until we're ready to persuade him not to start a war.

